data.description: Step into the realm of modern living, where every corner whispers of pristine elegance. This nearly new masterpiece is complete with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a beautiful kitchen that is an entertainer's dream boasting fresh stainless steel appliances. With a living space that stretches wide and has great sight lines into the kitchen and eating spaces, you'll appreciate the ambiance and warmth that radiates through the home. The Primary Suite is spacious, separating the bath from the bedroom with a barn door, adding an extra touch of character. The backyard is a blank canvas for you to make your own vision come to life. You don't want to miss this one!
